  <metadata>
    <name>VIA Chapter III — Offline POI Database</name>
    <desc>Campgrounds, drinking water, toilets and showers along the VIA Chapter III Ultima Thule route. Curated from OSM data. Covers NL → DE → DK → SE → NO. Supplement with live Overpass query for full coverage.</desc>
  </metadata>

